claim: The 2015 film Jurassic World generated five sequels.
premise_source_doc_sentence: Jurassic Park is considered a landmark in the development of computer-generated imagery and animatronic visual effects , and was followed by three commercially successful sequels , The Lost World : Jurassic Park  (  1997  )  , Jurassic Park III  (  2001  )  , and Jurassic World  (  2015  )  .
